§0      "Pursuing the§0
§0     American Meme"§0
§0
§0Governor of Arrakis, Cyrus, has begun construction on a new city in Arrakis, named Sikarra. Sikarra is an American western themed city, nestled in a valley near Arrakis’s southern shore. ...
#- Residents SpookySly, CaptainNemo123, HeckaJoe, and Rubikon have moved into Sikarra to assist with construction. For major contributions to the city, Governor Cyrus has appointed Rubikon as Chief Architect of §0Sikarra.If§0 you wish to check out the city, ...
#- Sikarra can be visited at the coordinates x:4644 z:-1345.
#- The following are paid advertisements.
#- §4Make Northhaven Home§0
§0In the northern regions of the Aquilan state of Garzweiler lies the construction site of a new luxury city. The aim of this city is to entertain the more experienced players & to provide excellent facilities for them to use. ...
#- The city is starting to take shape, & there is now a direct line to it from Aquila (Local Lines). Feel free to visit at any time! If you like what you see, and want to live there, you can get a prebuilt house or a plot.§0
§0~ Farrent
